{"tid":1855284,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"台灣政府投資增加口罩供應 3週內日產700萬片","createTime":"2020-02-01T04:18:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T07:05:09.000Z","uid":39464,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"ff471af7bb0eb74fe6d640eef7e0098bba86e2a7","tid":1855284,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:18:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://imgcdn.cna.com.tw/www/WebPhotos/1024/20200131/1200x900_803511714340.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgcdn.cna.com.tw%2Fwww%2FWebPhotos%2F1024%2F20200131%2F1200x900_803511714340.jpg&h=78bde523&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎疫情造成口罩供不應求，行政院長蘇貞昌今天拍板，將由政府出資近新台幣2億元建立口罩生產線，預計3週後每日全台口罩生產量可增為700萬片，約4到5週後可達每日1000萬片。<br />\n<br />\n政院官員今天表示，國內目前口罩產量約每日400萬片，因蘇貞昌要求提高到日產600萬片，經濟部長沈榮津日前已向廠商訪價，希望建立口罩生產線。<br />\n<br />\n政院官員說，沈榮津與廠商洽談過程中，都將細節即時回報給蘇貞昌，今天下午蘇貞昌與副院長陳其邁、秘書長李孟諺交換意見後，認為防疫視同作戰，兵貴神速，立刻拍板決定，指示沈榮津今天就跟廠商談定，越快越好。<br />\n<br />\n官員說，政府將投入2億元建立口罩生產線，預估3週後可以每天增加口罩產量300萬片，約4週到5週後每日增加600萬片，總產量可達到每日1000萬片。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202001310351.aspx\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cna.com.tw%2Fnews%2Ffirstnews%2F202001310351.aspx&d=HQiZr%2BzFLDuBt%2FA%2FXRO5IlNDr8uFEZb%2F0ofPPvrEBCw%3D&h=59bec9cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cna.com.tw/news/firstnews/202001310351.aspx</a>"},{"pid":"18c60f8bcb11f9bd7a07da2394d2f60847b30bdc","tid":1855284,"uid":33437,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"人地台灣都可以日產1000萬個，<br />\n世界第二大經濟體點會唔夠口罩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"847ddc08186f1d795df0e71cd7ada97a4d65e274","tid":1855284,"uid":30040,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"18c60f8bcb11f9bd7a07da2394d2f60847b30bdc","tid":1855284,"uid":33437,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T04:23:10.000Z","msg":"人地台灣都可以日產1000萬個，<br />\n世界第二大經濟體點會唔夠口罩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:28:55.000Z","msg":"佢地自己故意炒口罩，乜都有得炒"},{"pid":"72273c2102aac3593e6a00278c5a3bc237b36dc1","tid":1855284,"uid":118694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:29:51.000Z","msg":"呢啲政府先係做到野既政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c67903bf4eca18a263de8e2af4857ad1c5692db","tid":1855284,"uid":53811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:30:36.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以考慮台灣供應穩定之後，買條香港生產線？支持台貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9debc4027272fa9595201c234c6f322674d33a02","tid":1855284,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c67903bf4eca18a263de8e2af4857ad1c5692db","tid":1855284,"uid":53811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:30:36.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以考慮台灣供應穩定之後，買條香港生產線？支持台貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:39:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n日產1000萬都係唔夠人地分全民口罩用一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31876bcbff3266010328ed852c2c5de315978621","tid":1855284,"uid":81140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:43:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"161351ea4d7850a332265c32cf7f2e9310b51dfb","tid":1855284,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9debc4027272fa9595201c234c6f322674d33a02","tid":1855284,"uid":25424,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0c67903bf4eca18a263de8e2af4857ad1c5692db","tid":1855284,"uid":53811,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-01T05:30:36.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以考慮台灣供應穩定之後，買條香港生產線？支持台貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cited